'''''Kairasikkaran''''' (English: Man with the midas touch) is a [[1984 in film|1984]] [[Tamil language|Tamil]] Indian feature film directed by SSK Shankar for SKS Films. The film stars [[Prabhu Ganesan]] and [[Radha (actress)|Radha]] in the lead roles.<ref>{{cite web|title=Kairasikkaran LP Vinyl Records|url=http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers/384/3/1/1|publisher=musicalaya|accessdate=2014-05-02|}}</ref>

== Cast ==

*[[Prabhu Ganesan]]
*[[Radha (actress)|Radha]]
*[[Silk Smitha]]
*[[Y. G. Mahendra]]
==Soundtrack==
Soundtrack was composed by Ilaiyaraja.<ref>https://bollywoodvinyl.in/collections/kannada-malayalam-telugu-tamil-lps/products/kairasikkaran-tamil-bollywood-vinyl-lp</ref>
*Nilavondru - [[S. P. Balasubrahmanyam|SPB]], [[S. Janaki]]
*Kai Veesum - SPB, S Janaki
*Oomaimegame - Ilayaraja
*Hey Raja - S Janaki
*Then Sumandha - SPB

